        div(id='about', class='blurb')
            h3(style='text-align: center;') About Us
            hr
            p Been Drinkin' is a 20-man raiding guild on Mal'Ganis-US focused on mythic raiding on a 2 days (8 hours) per week schedule.
            p Our raid times are:<br>&bull; Tuesday: 7:30 to 11:30 PM CST (Server)<br>&bull; Wednesday: 7:30 to 11:30 PM CST (Server)<br>&bull; Friday Alt-run: 5:30 to 8:30 PM CST (Server)<br>
            p The majority of our members are old school ex-hardcore players and real-life friends; most of whom have been raiding and gaming together for many years and have extensive raiding experience ranging back to Vanilla. In the past, we've raided 5 days a week over a 30 hour schedule and cleared end-game content prior to easy-mode nerfs across multiple expansions.
            p Contrary to that statement, we understand that people have lives; jobs, school, partners, children, etc. Mythic progression raiding <b>shouldn't require personal sacrifice outside of WoW.</b> It is this philosophy that Been Drinkin' was founded upon.
            p We're recruiting talented individuals that enjoy raiding, with the skill and the dedication to better themselves and the others around them; that hold our own beliefs and ideas themselves. We look forward to raiding, kicking ass, and having fun while doing it all.
            p We use Discord for team communication, stream all raid fights over Twitch, and prefer our whiskey neat.
            hr

